<item>
            <title>[LU-14760] short read when aio cross stripe</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14760</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;short read could happen for aio when:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;we are reading cross the stripe&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;layout lock got cancelled on client before we continue to next stripe in cl_io_loop()&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;vvp_io_read_start()-&amp;gt;can_populate_pages() sees the layout has changed, marks the io needs to be restarted.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ll_file_io_generic failed to restart io as the return code from cl_io_loop() is EIOCBQUEUED.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
